Rational Interaction Opportunities: Sr. Dev Ops Engineer

Hi Brian,

I'm currently working on a role for our client at Microsoft, that I think you would be a good fit for. I'd love to connect via phone and tell you more about the role and being part of Rational. 

If you're interested, please send me few days/times and best number to reach you on and I'll schedule that in the calendar. 
Please note that I work in Pacific Time Zone.

You can also send your resume to: rena@rationalagency.com 

Looking forward to hearing back.

Best,
Rena Cunningham
